flex justify-between items-start"><span class="text-sm text-fg-faint leading-tight">ba</span><span class="text-sm text-fg-faint font-mono shrink-0">0.1.6</span></span><span class="block text-2xl font-light tracking-display font-display leading-tight truncate">sample-wasi-http-rust</span><span class="block text-sm text-fg-muted mt-6 overflow-hidden" style="display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; min-height: 2.75rem">A sample WASI HTTP component written in Rust</span></a></div></div></div></div></div>
